    <section id="about-story" class="about-story-section-k847">
        <div class="content-container-max-tx92">
            <h2 class="section-title-h2-847k">Our Journey Began</h2>
            <div class="story-grid-layout-tx92">
                <div class="story-text-content-92k">
                    <p>Founded by passionate travelers who understood the struggle of packing light while staying stylish, TravixoHub emerged from a simple need: clothing that works as hard as you do.</p>
                    <p>We believe every woman deserves to feel confident and comfortable, whether she's exploring ancient ruins in Greece or attending a business meeting in Tokyo. Our carefully curated pieces blend functionality with feminine style.</p>
                    <p>From wrinkle-resistant fabrics to versatile designs that transition from day to night, every item in our collection tells a story of thoughtful design and quality craftsmanship.</p>
                </div>
